# Backend Services

The `services/` directory contains backend microservices that power the Zeiro platform.

## User Service

The Users service in [services/users](mdc:services/users) handles user management, including:
- User registration
- User profile management
- User permissions and roles

## Authentication Service

The Authentication service in [services/authentication](mdc:services/authentication) handles:
- User login and logout
- Token management
- Session handling
- Authentication workflows
